@AppHost_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001

### Create Patient
POST {{AppHost_HostAddress}}/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "createdBy": 1,
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-05-15",
  "gender": 0,
  "ethnicityId": 1,
  "healthInsuranceNumber": "DN1234567890",
  "createdAt": "2025-02-05T10:30:00Z"
}

### Create Medical Record (No PDF)
POST {{AppHost_HostAddress}}/api/medical-records
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="PatientId"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="RecordType"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="MedicalCode"

MR12345
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="AdmissionDiagnosis"

Viêm họng cấp
--boundary--

### Create Medical Record (With PDF)
# Note: Ensure the file path exists on your machine
POST {{AppHost_HostAddress}}/api/medical-records
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="PatientId"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="RecordType"

2
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="MedicalCode"

MR67890
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="AdmissionDiagnosis"

Chấn thương chỉnh hình
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="PdfFiles"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< C:/path/to/your/sample.pdf
--boundary--
